Assembly Definition Files (ADF)
=> one DDL per script
=> (default without ADF): everything recompiled on every changes

Hierarchies
=> changes are tracked per hierarchy
=> multi-thread

Cheat function
=> speed-up development
=> use that function before a function [Condition(DEVELOPMENT_BUILD || UNITY_EDITOR)] (ignore in production build)
=> wrap code in this (aside from functions) #if DEVELOPMENT_BUILD || UNITY_EDITOR #endif

Test Scenes
=> test a single feature
=> check new features didn't broke old features